cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.IT, cs.LG 

This paper deals with image and video processing, specifically with the removal of specular reflections. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses low-rank representation and variational methods, which are common in machine learning (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.GR, cs.IT). Finally, the paper presents experimental results and compares its approach with existing methods, which suggests a focus on evaluation and performance analysis (cs.LG).
